title: A Look at Potential First-Time All-Stars
description:
This week, Kyle and Tyler kick off the show by discussing Victor Wembanyama and what he can be if he’s healthy (5:00). Then, they discuss the new-look Timberwolves and how much better Anthony Edwards can get with Rudy Gobert on his team (11:07), plus Cade Cunningham’s chance of being an All-Star this year. (29:00)

Hosts: J. Kyle Mann and Tyler Parker
Producer: Brian H. Waters
